<section class="demo-hero">
  <div class="demo-hero__content">
    <span class="demo-hero__badge">Modulo Demo</span>
    <h1 class="demo-hero__title">Experimenta un Modulo Ewaffle</h1>
    <p class="demo-hero__subtitle">No te lo contamos. Te lo mostramos.</p>
    <p class="demo-hero__desc">Cada recurso que ves aqui es exactamente lo que producimos para nuestros clientes. Video, guia interactiva, simulacion gamificada e infografia — todo funcional, todo real.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .demo-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a5e 55%, #e91e8c 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 80px 24px 60px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    isolation: isolate;
  }
  .demo-hero::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: -20% auto auto -15%;
    width: 340px;
    height: 340px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.18), transparent 68%);
    filter: blur(12px);
    animation: shimmer-drift 14s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) infinite alternate;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  .demo-hero::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    right: -90px;
    bottom: -120px;
    width: 320px;
    height: 320px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(247,201,72,0.18), transparent 70%);
    filter: blur(8px);
    animation: shimmer-drift 18s cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1) infinite alternate-reverse;
    z-index: -1;
  }
  .demo-hero__content {
    max-width: 780px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .demo-hero__badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 6px 18px;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .demo-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .demo-hero__subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 22px);
    opacity: 0.92;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .demo-hero__desc {
    font-size: 16px;
    opacity: 0.78;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  @keyframes shimmer-drift {
    from { transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0) scale(1); }
    to { transform: translate3d(18px, 22px, 0) scale(1.08); }
  }
</style>
